Transcription.Text: By Trevor Williams. A move to stop Mr. Gaitskell from nominating any more Labour life Peers is to be made at a meeting of Labour M Ps tomorrow. Mr. Michael Foot has put down a resolution on the subject and he is to be backed by Mr Will Griffiths, MP for Manchester Exchange.
